snippet: Young gun Grigor Dimitrov stands between Andy Murray and the Wimbledon semi-finals and the champion is clearly wary of the Bulgarian he describes as "coming into his prime"....

headline.print_headline: Champion Murray in a Hurry on Center Court
headline.main: Champion Murray in a Hurry on Center Court

lead_paragraph: Young gun Grigor Dimitrov stands between Andy Murray and the Wimbledon semi-finals and the champion is clearly wary of the Bulgarian he describes as "coming into his prime".
